      <div>
        <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid">
          <div class="container">
            <h1 class="display-3">Time to plan!</h1>
            <p class="lead">Fill out these simple questions and we will create the perfect itinerary for you!</p>
            <hr class="my-2">
            <p >If you need to inspiration, click here!</p>
